14.3.6 Retaining Your Personal Information
We have policies and practices requiring the secure deletion of personal information when there is no applicable regulatory retention requirement and we no longer have a business need to use the information for a purpose that is compatible with our disclosed purposes of collection. Personal information that has been aggregated or deidentified so that it cannot reasonably be used to infer information about you or otherwise be linked to you may be retained indefinitely.
14.4 Opt Out Signals
California law requires us to let you know how we respond to web browser Do Not Track (DNT) signals. Our websites will respond to a Do Not Track Signal by not placing tracking technologies that are not necessary to deliver the Klarna Services to you on your browser. These preferences are managed at the browser level, and are not “frictionless” as defined by California law. You can find information about how to manage Opt Out Signal settings in your browser, and other information in
Section 7
“How can you restrict us from sharing your Personal Information?".
14.5 Notice of Financial Incentive
We may offer customers the opportunity to participate in various incentive, referral, loyalty, or other promotional programs (collectively “Programs”) related to the collection, retention, sharing or sale of your personal information. By participating in the Programs, you may earn benefits such as gift cards, vouchers, discounts and other valuable offers. These benefits may be considered “financial incentives” or “price or service difference” under the CCPA. These Programs may involve collecting the following categories of Personal Information from customers who participate: customer identifiers; customer records; protected class and demographic information; purchase or transaction information; internet or other electronic network activity information and device information; audio, electronic, visual, or other sensory information; and inferences from such information. We are providing you with this information so that you may make an informed decision on whether to participate in any Program.
When you sign-up for the Programs, you opt-in to receive such financial incentives. We may also collect certain personal information in connection with Programs that we used to administer the Program and provide you Program benefits, and to understand your interaction with Klarna Services so that we may improve our products and services and notify you of offers and promotions that may be of interest to you.
By participating in any such Program, you agree that the financial incentives offered in connection with the Programs are reasonably related to the value of the personal information  collected and retained in connection with the Programs.
